<collectingCountry id="F35C7638FFD3FFCFFE65FB3EFD2F0CB9" box="[410,763,1243,1265]" name="Democratic Republic of the Congo" pageId="17" pageNumber="568">Democratic Republic of the Congo</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFDA4B59FFD3FFCFFCF6FB3EFC760CB9" author="HERMAN L" box="[777,930,1243,1265]" pageId="17" pageNumber="568" pagination="2441 - 3020" refId="ref20546" refString="HERMAN L. H. (2001): Catalog of the Staphylinidae (Insecta, Coleoptera); 1758 to the end of the second Millennium. V Staphylinine group (Part 2): Diochini, Maorothiini, Othiini, Platyprosopini, Staphylinini (Amblyopinina, Anisolinina, Hyptiomina, Philonthina). - Bulletin of the American Museum of Natural History 265: 2441 - 3020." type="journal article" year="2001">HERMAN 2001</bibRefCitation>
